## Volume Mounts

Sample data mount configuration:
- **Host path**: `<project-root>/sample-data/`
- **Container path**: `/Volumes/main/default/geobrix_samples/`
- **Data location**: `/Volumes/main/default/geobrix_samples/geobrix-examples/`

